text: Nephus ornatus, the ornate lady beetle, is a species of dusky lady beetle in the family Coccinellidae. It is found in North America. ==Subspecies== * Nephus ornatus naviculatus (Casey, 1899) * Nephus ornatus ornatus (LeConte, 1850) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * Category:Coccinellidae Category:Beetles described in 1850
title: Nephus ornatus
